title: Naga Panchami
subTitle: A man kills his sister and throws her family into disarray. However, his sister's daughter, a shape-shifting snake, is determined to seek revenge.

title: Gorosthaney Sabdhan
subTitle: Three friends investigate the vandalism of a grave and the theft of a clock.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainavati exercises her authority over Parvati. Determined to marry Parvati, Tarakasur reveals his true colours and forces her to comply.

title: Bangshadhar
subTitle: Jamindar Khokon Chowdhuri's father is killed by his younger brother Pwena. His wife looks after his business and what follows is a feud with regard to their property.

title: Sathi Amar
subTitle: After his parents' death, Raja takes care of his sister and falls in love with one of her friends, Jyoti. He attempts his best to win over his lover.

title: Le Halua Le
subTitle: Sonali moves to the city to earn money and repay her debts to her landlord. She fakes a marriage with Suvojeet, a struggling artist, in order to get low-priced accommodation.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: After his wife's demise, a man tries to start over with her estranged family. When he falls in love with his wife's twin, he fears that his efforts to mend broken relations will go to waste.

title: Pratibad
subTitle: A fierce fighter against injustice strives to help his middle-class family make ends meet. His dedication lands him a job as a police officer, where he tackles large-scale problems with determination.

title: Poran Jaye Jolia Re
subTitle: A young man, Rabin, meets three different women at different stages in his life. The relationship he shares with these women, though very different from each other, help him grow as a person.

title: Premi
subTitle: Sumit, a football player, loses his leg while trying to save Rahul, his best friend. Fate plays a cruel joke when the girl Rahul loves is about to be married off to Sumit.

title: Premi
subTitle: Sumit, a football player, loses his leg while trying to save Rahul, his best friend. Fate plays a cruel joke when the girl Rahul loves is about to be married off to Sumit.

title: Toke Chhara Banchbo Na
subTitle: Arjun meets Hiya, his childhood sweetheart, and falls in love with her. However, his past haunts him and his relationship with Hiya suffers.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati desperately tries to evade Tarakasur's unwelcome advances. Feeling cornered and finding no help in sight, Parvati attacks Tarakasur with Lord Shiva's trident.

title: Ora Charjon
subTitle: Destiny unites four strangers who are imprisoned under a false charge. Together, the four men escape prison and embark on a quest for revenge.

title: Tomake Chai
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Champion
subTitle: Jones, a talented and disciplined footballer, is judged by his peers for his financial status. However, when he finds out about his past, he faces a dilemma.

title: Premer Kahini
subTitle: Akash falls in love with Barsha but loses contact with her due to unforeseeable circumstances. While attending a marriage ceremony, he is shocked to realise that the bride is none other than Barsha.

title: Nayak - The Real Hero
subTitle: Joy aspires to be a police inspector like his father, an honest police constable. As his father meets the local anti-social thug, the situation shifts and conflicts arise.

title: Sedin Dekha Hoyechilo
subTitle: Kavita's father holds his daughter's lover's friends captive and asks them to reveal the couple's whereabouts. However, one of the boys, Abir, falls in love with his other daughter, Nandini.

title: Jhinuk Mala
subTitle: Sujan and Sakhi are madly in love with each other and want to spend their lives together. However, Sakhi's vicious stepmother has other plans for them.

title: Jhinuk Mala

title: The Bongs Again
subTitle: Two young women arrive in new cities in order to look for their parents. However, their journeys cause them to develop a new perspective towards their lives.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Shukracharya intervenes in the battle to rescue Tarakasura, and Himavan is aware of Parvati's love towards Lord Shiva.

title: Aami Sei Meye
subTitle: Sagar, the son of a millionaire, falls in love with Bristhi. Later, things get intense when she gets molested by a friend of Sagar.

title: Yugavatar Lokenath
subTitle: The wealthy Dutta family's priest narrates the miracles and teachings of Baba Lokenath and stresses on the importance of harmony in order to make way for reconciliation.

title: Apon Holo Por
subTitle: Madhabi is cast out by her husband, Abhijit, after a false accusation of rape. Years later, she reunites with him, determined to prove her innocence and uncover the truth behind the tragic misunderstanding.

title: Sangee
subTitle: When Bijay comes to Calcutta for higher studies, he meets Rupa and instantly falls in love with her. However, he is unaware that she is his friend Rana's sister.

title: Surya
subTitle: Ashok, a businessman, provides shelter to Mahim Halden who kills and takes over his property. Soon, Ashok's son, Surya, sets out to avenge his father's death.

title: Satrur Muqubila
subTitle: Awbhoy, a dedicated police officer, develops a deep romantic interest in a young woman attending a job interview while undergoing training.

title: Badsha: The Don
